$ Windows

Windows is a *symetric multiprocessing OS*: all → hardware/CPU[CPUs] are equal, the → Windows/kernel[Windows kernel] can schedule a → Windows/development/process[process] to run on any processor.

→ Windows/Appearance/Mouse[Mouse appearance]

