{ Configuring Windows #windows-configuring

   Windows can be configured through different methods:
    • → Windows/settings[settings]
    • → Windows/control-panel[control panel]
    • → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/mmc_exe[Microsoft Management Console (MMC)]

   Generally, a → Windows/control-panel#control-panel-item[control panel item] is aimed for general users while an MMC snap-in is targeted at IT professionals.

